org.slc.sli.dashboard.manager
Interface PopulationManager

All Known Implementing Classes:
PopulationManagerImpl
public interface PopulationManager

Facilitates creation of logical aggregations of EdFi entities/associations such as a student summary comprised of student profile, program, and assessment information in order to deliver the Population Summary interaction.
